---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import "../style/global.css";
const siteTitle = "sponsor theo";
const description = "want to sponsor theo? here's everything you need to know";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <meta name="description" content={description} />
    <meta name="twitter:image" content="https://t3.gg/images/twitter.png" />
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
    <meta name="twitter:creator" content="@t3dotgg" />
    <meta property="og:title" content={siteTitle} />
    <meta property="og:description" content={description} />
    <meta property="og:image" content="https://t3.gg/images/twitter.png" />
    <title>{siteTitle}</title>
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#000000" />

    <script defer data-domain="astro.t3.gg" src="/js/script.js"></script>
  </head>
  <body class="h-screen bg-white text-black">
    <main class="pb-2 md:py-2">
      <article class="prose prose-lg lg:prose-xl mx-auto max-w-[800px] px-2">
        <section>
          <blockquote>
            <p>
              Someday I&apos;ll have to tell you how transformational these ads
              have been for us. Our biggest worry is how we will service all the
              new clients going into 2025.
            </p>
            <p>
              We did other ads in 2024, but <span class="font-bold"
                >the Theo ads were by far the most effective for us</span
              >. It&apos;s clear to us that you in particular get it - exactly
              what we need.
            </p>
            <div class="not-prose flex items-center gap-3">
              <img
                src={"/assets/sponsors/infinite-red.svg"}
                alt={"Infinite Red"}
                class="h-12 w-12 object-contain"
              />
              <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">
                Jamon<span class="text-slate-600"
                  >, <a href="https://infinitered.com" target="_blank"
                    >Infinite Red</a
                  ></span
                >
              </p>
            </div>
          </blockquote>
        </section>
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold">sponsoring theo</h2>
          <p>
            hi! i'm theo. you probably know me from <a
              href="https://youtube.com/@t3dotgg">youtube</a
            >. if you want experienced devs to know something, i'm a pretty good
            way to make that happen.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h3>why sponsor theo?</h3>
          <p>
            good developers watch my videos to learn about new technologies. my
            audience is so excited to learn about new tech that they <em
              >often like the ads more than the videos themselves</em
            >
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <Image
            alt="sponsor comments"
            src={"https://ezkf3xv6eh.ufs.sh/f/3odeDX4eRzTNQlTj6vGY8AzxSWdivlGJ0fNusyEU7bKQDZBH"}
            onclick={`window.open('https://ezkf3xv6eh.ufs.sh/f/3odeDX4eRzTNQlTj6vGY8AzxSWdivlGJ0fNusyEU7bKQDZBH', '_blank')`}
            width={800}
            height={400}
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </section>

        <section>
          <h3>the numbers</h3>
          <p>
            i'm in the <a
              href="https://socialblade.com/youtube/c/theobrowne1017"
              target="_blank">top 2000 youtubers in the US</a
            >. we get <strong>over 3 million views per month</strong>, often
            breaking <strong>400,000 watch hours</strong> (~2 super bowl commercials).
          </p>
          <p>
            my channel has significantly more reach than branded content
            reasonably should. big brands on youtube (like <a
              href="https://socialblade.com/youtube/c/vercelhq"
              target="_blank">vercel</a
            >) have <strong>less than 5% of my reach</strong>.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h3>demographics</h3>
          <p>
            this isn't a bunch of beginners learning to code - my audience
            actually ships. <strong>76% of them are over 25</strong>. the most
            recent state of react survey showed that <em
              >over half of react devs watch my videos.</em
            >
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <p>
            i've helped <a href="/sponsors"
              >over 40 brands grow their businesses</a
            > - will yours be next?
          </p>
          <h3></h3>
        </section>

        <section>
          <p>
            email us at
            <span class="font-semibold">youtube @ (this domain)</span> for more info
            on pricing and availability
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <blockquote>
            <p>
              I always know when you guys publish something because we have a
              slack channel with new signups and <span class="font-semibold"
                >it&apos;s getting flooded.</span
              >
            </p>

            <div class="not-prose flex items-center gap-3">
              <img
                src={"/assets/sponsors/sevalla.svg"}
                alt={"Sevalla"}
                width={96}
                height={96}
                class="h-12 w-12 object-contain"
              />
              <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">
                Paul<span class="text-slate-600"
                  >, <a href="https://sevalla.com" target="_blank">Sevalla</a
                  ></span
                >
              </p>
            </div>
          </blockquote>
        </section>

        <section>
          <a
            href="/"
            class="flex items-center gap-1 text-gray-500 hover:underline"
          >
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="h-4 w-4"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width={2}
                d="M10 19l-7-7m0 0l7-7m-7 7h18"></path>
            </svg>
            back to theo's site
          </a>
        </section>
      </article>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
